<p class="">I announced the necessity for this change 12 months ago, and I have <span id="1269" class="column-number" data-column-number="1269"></span> given careful consideration to the matter since. The pedestal in Trafalgar Square has not yet been moved. It is necessary to remove it quickly, but I can put off the decision in regard to the new site for the statue for some time yet.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
